imdb.plot outline: The Noite with Danilo Gentili is a Brazilian television program produced and originally screened by SBT, which is presented by stand-up comedian Danilo Gentili. It is a late-night talk show, with the presence of humor and late night entertainment. The show started on March 10, 2014, and since then has been airing during five days of the week, around midnight.
imdb.title: The Noite com Danilo Gentili
plot: A talk show in the night!

The Noite with Danilo Gentili is a Brazilian television program produced and originally screened by SBT, which is presented by stand-up comedian Danilo Gentili. It is a late-night talk show, with the presence of humor and late night entertainment. The show started on March 10, 2014, and since then has been airing during five days of the week, around midnight.
